characters.name: Rickard Karstark
characters.description: Rickard Karstark is the Lord of Karhold and the head of House Karstark, a vassal family to House Stark of Winterfell.

characters.name: Jon Arryn
characters.description: Jon Arryn was the Lord of the Eyrie and the head of House Arryn, one of the Great Houses of Westeros.

characters.name: Ser Hugh
characters.description: Hugh served as Lord Jon Arryn's squire for four years before Jon Arryn's death.

characters.name: Maester Cressen
characters.description: Cressen was the Maester of Dragonstone and a servant of Stannis Baratheon.

characters.name: Torrhen Karstark
characters.description: Torrhen is a son of Lord Rickard Karstark, the Lord of Karhold.

characters.name: Janos Slynt
characters.description: Janos Slynt is the commander of the King Landing City Watch, with almost two thousand men under his command.

characters.name: Karl Tanner
characters.description: Karl Tanner was a brother of the Night Watch who had gone north of the Wall on Lord Commander Mormont's Great Ranging.
